itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[804] 係堅尼地城/西環有需要落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d284a6685c2a68d3ccd09fb4a6b70dfb7b77c186","tid":1406753,"uid":246200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"d35c1c8a2766ec79922f22c59df23b22299a184c","tid":1406753,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"- 游擊戰，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，4方配合。<br />\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。<br />\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守，如果見到狗察完成佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地。<br />\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到敵方，盡快設路障或陷阱後就退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，不要企硬對峙，不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊。<br />\n- 盡量聽同伴意見，不被捕，不被包圍。"},{"pid":"9e7b9dc2482fdf3c90299fe7c6267e2c9b5fda3e","tid":1406753,"uid":246200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a885b294abbe5325dcd10537d490d1b0c491c127","tid":1406753,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13a16d344298258f59af6966acf64e52d50bfd2","tid":1406753,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔好去黃大仙<br />\n多狗"},{"pid":"00b6fa42ecb21847235c504f45534d00c144d6f1","tid":1406753,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b8b83338876a770e2ff55ea9